    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Take your <strong>steak[s] </strong>out of the fridge, open the packet and let them adjust to room temperature and boil a kettle</p><p>Heat a dry, large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat</p><p>Pat your <strong>rump steak[s]</strong> dry with<strong> </strong>kitchen<strong> </strong>paper, add a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
