      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>beef stock mix </strong>with 250ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[375ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[500ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>couscous</strong> to a large heatproof bowl with your <strong>diced apricots</strong>, <strong>ras el hanout </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Add the <strong>beef stock</strong>, then cover and set aside – this is your <strong>fruity spiced couscous</strong></p>",
